reviewText: My niece has been looking for this Scooby Do n Mexico and could not find it. She loved it and the other one that came with it.
We are big Scooby fans here at my house. Love these DVDs. I will buy more.
Great double feature, I love Scooby doo,
Scooby doo usually has good cartoons. This was no different. Had these on cassette but had to get them on dvd.
My son loves Scooby, He loves this DVD
My son really enjoys these movies and it was a great price too!
Love adding to the collection on DVD
